<li class='cover' id='bookCover_10605'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/10605.Thinner"><img alt="Thinner" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1554308961l/10605._SY160_.jpg" />
